OL,3,CCharity run that barred women and
OL,4,Cgirls over 12 'reviewing its policies'
OL,6,FA charity run that stopped women and
OL,7,Fgirls over 12 from taking part is
OL,8,F"reviewing its policies" after a
OL,9,Fbacklash.
OL,11,FThe Muslim Charity Run, held in
OL,12,FLondon's Victoria Park last month, was
OL,13,Fbilled as an "inclusive 5km race"
OL,14,Fwelcoming "runners and supporters of
OL,15,Fall ages and abilities", but it was
OL,16,Fopen only to "men, boys of all ages
OL,17,Fand girls under 12".
