OL,3,CCharity run that barred women and
OL,4,Cgirls over 12 'reviewing its policies'
OL,6,FA Muslim women's group said the event
OL,7,Fshould have been more inclusive to
OL,8,Favoid "reinforcement of negative
OL,9,Fstereotypes".
OL,11,FOrganised by East London Mosque and
OL,12,Fthe London Muslim Centre, it was said
OL,13,Fto have attracted hundreds of runners
OL,14,Fand supporters.
OL,16,FIn an update on Sunday, the Equality
OL,17,Fand Human Rights Commission said it
OL,18,Fwould not take any further action.
