OL,3,CCharity run that barred women and
OL,4,Cgirls over 12 'reviewing its policies'
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We recognise
OL,7,Fthat the organisers have committed to
OL,8,Freviewing their policies and the
OL,9,Fformat of the event in advance of the
OL,10,Fnext Muslim Charity Run.
OL,12,F"If we are made aware of any further
OL,13,Fcomplaints about the event, we stand
OL,14,Fready to re-examine the concerns and
OL,15,Ftake action where appropriate.
OL,17,F"We also have guidance available on
OL,18,Fcompliance with the Equality Act 2010
OL,19,Fto help the organisers avoid unlawful
OL,20,Fdiscrimination and ensure their events
OL,21,Fare inclusive."
