OL,3,CCharity run that barred women and
OL,4,Cgirls over 12 'reviewing its policies'
OL,6,FCommunities Secretary Steve Reed
OL,7,Fcriticised the exclusion of women and
OL,8,Folder girls, saying he was "horrified"
OL,9,Fand "appalled".
OL,11,FHe told LBC Radio last month:
OL,12,F"Speaking for myself, I was appalled.
OL,14,F"We do not want a situation in this
OL,15,Fcountry where men are allowed to do
OL,16,Fthings that women are then barred
OL,17,Ffrom. We cannot tolerate that."
