OL,3,CCharity run that barred women and
OL,4,Cgirls over 12 'reviewing its policies'
OL,6,FThe annual event is described on the
OL,7,Fmosque website as having become a
OL,8,F"highlight in the east London Muslim
OL,9,Fcalendar, raising thousands of pounds
OL,10,Ffor vital causes across the UK and
OL,11,Fabroad, from local youth projects,
OL,12,Ffood banks and refugee support to
OL,13,Finternational humanitarian relief".
OL,15,FOctober's event was the 12th annual
OL,16,FMuslim Charity Run.
OL,18,FEast London Mosque has been approached
OL,19,Ffor comment.
